title: Eboni K Williams Interview and More

description:
Today on the show we had Eboni K. Williams stop by and she spoke on on leaving fox news, political narratives, Jussie Smollett's case  and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to another Florida man, and this time it was because he threatened police with an army, but not humans; instead it was an army of turtles,  you know the craziest people live in Florida and the  Bronx. Moreover, Angela also helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
